Package model.network

Class ChatServer

java.lang.Object
model.network.ChatServer
public class ChatServer
extends java.lang.Object
Holds a pool of UserThreads, provides methods for broadcasting to single user or all users Holds the game-object, provides methods for interacting with the game. (Start, Join, etc.)
Author:
Josef, Dennis, Yashar
